{"tid":1760794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：香港離普選特首更近或更遠相信大家自有判斷","createTime":"2019-11-28T12:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:33:42.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"914a702eb06452b7716e1c95de45129fef40d72e","tid":1760794,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"立法會三讀通過選舉條例修訂，涉及更新部分功能組別的團體清單資料，以及修訂候選人免付郵資投寄信件的厚度和尺寸要求等。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，雖然今次一系列修訂並非重大改變，但相信對助選工作有幫助。<span style=\"color: red;\">至於普選立法會的進展，聶德權表示，需要先落實特首普選，才能由普選的特首落實立法會普選</span>。他說，本港在一國基礎下實行兩制，各界對如此重要的憲制秩序充份了解和達成共識前，加上在近年社會情況，香港究竟離普選特首更近抑或更遠，相信大家自有判斷。<br />\n<br />\n對於區議會選舉，聶德權說，明白議員的關注，選管會會小心聆聽並提交報告，以檢視選舉安排及提出建議。他表示今次選舉票站眾多，工作人員亦多，相信培訓方面有改善空間。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495002-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495002-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=aa2b7a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495002-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aeb11ed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495002-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7899a8241f73b41d09e7a3513aef41a8055b0ec2","tid":1760794,"uid":95577,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"更近<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532e6728c13ab362846c5ca586f3780a0f666840","tid":1760794,"uid":167548,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"你地冚家鏟就肯定唔遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23477ca748e8e586313690d90242d85a544cffab","tid":1760794,"uid":35580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"係咪都冇架啦 攬炒啦仆街"},{"pid":"cb9c34e5a0697e8c9a95a24d4ea9084